entries.name: The Lord of the Rings
entries.description: The Lord of the Rings is a fantasy epic about a hobbit named Frodo Baggins who is tasked with destroying the One Ring, a powerful artifact that could bring about the end of the world. He sets out on a perilous journey with a group of companions to destroy the ring in the fires of Mount Doom.

entries.name: The Witcher
entries.description: The Witcher is a dark fantasy series based on the book series of the same name by Andrzej Sapkowski. It follows the adventures of Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter who roams the land in search of his destiny, encountering various dangerous creatures and people along the way.

entries.name: The Mandalorian
entries.description: The Mandalorian is a space western series set in the Star Wars universe. It follows the adventures of a lone bounty hunter, known only as the Mandalorian, as he travels across the galaxy, taking on various missions and encounters a mysterious creature known as The Child.
